{# Off-Screen Life - What a dismissed follower did while the player was away #}
{% if render_mode == "transform" or render_mode == "full" or render_mode == "thoughts" %}
{% if actorUUID and actorUUID != 0 %}
{% set actor = decnpc(actorUUID) %}
{% if actor and actor.UUID %}
{% set is_fol = is_follower(actorUUID) or is_sever_follower(actorUUID) %}
{% set was_follower = sever_was_follower(actor.UUID) %}
{% if not is_fol and was_follower %}
{% set home_loc = default(sever_home(actor.UUID), "") %}
{% set event_history = sever_life_event_history(actor.UUID) %}
{% set life_summary = sever_life_summary(actor.UUID) %}
{% if event_history != "" or life_summary != "" %}

## What You've Been Up To
{% if home_loc != "" %}
Since {{ player.name }} left, you've been living in {{ home_loc }}.
{% else %}
Since {{ player.name }} went their separate way, you've been on your own.
{% endif %}
{% if event_history != "" %}
Your recent days:
{{ event_history }}
{% elif life_summary != "" %}
Recently: {{ life_summary }}
{% endif %}

These are YOUR real memories of what you did — you lived through them. When talking to {{ player.name }} or others, you can reference these naturally if the topic comes up. Don't recite the full list — just mention whatever is relevant to the conversation. Significant and notable events left a stronger impression on you.
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% endif %}